name: Maul
description: The son of Dathomere was turned into a Dark Lord of the Sith by Darth Sidious. After his body was cut in half by Obi Wan Kenobi, he nearly died.  The Night Sisters of Dathomere created a new body for him with darkside magic.  Then he spent his years ruling crime syndicates and seeking revenge.  His revenge led him to his final demise (by Obi Wan Kenobi)..
